{"tid":1116621,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"可能係連登第一個Discord電台","createTime":"2019-04-20T06:35:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T19:13:01.000Z","uid":43718,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"cc66e05c7d8384859a675d872d85a301842f9e10","tid":1116621,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T06:35:07.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">前言</span></div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">最近發現Discord原來有個bot可以一路播歌 一路傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁啱小弟喺外國身邊又無咩做 所以想睇下有無巴絲打同我一樣無咩嘢做 又想搵嘢聽下 咪入黎傾下計吹下水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果巴絲打有心事感情學業工作煩惱都可以係度分享 睇下咁其他巴打有無咩意見畀到你咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n得閒仲可以點下歌開心share大家音樂既興趣 無聊想廢up下都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最緊要係要禁入嚟睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">-----------------------------------------------------</div><br />\n<br />\n而家已經有超過<span style=\"color: red;\">「<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>350</strong></span>」</span>個巴絲打入咗頻道啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今晚嘅開台時間大約係<span style=\"color: violet;\">「<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2300-0200</span></strong>」</span> <br />\n<br />\n有興趣就入嚟聽聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲可以試下Call-In<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n傳送門: <a href=\"https://discord.gg/qFTfqpc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FqFTfqpc&d=v6UOKjiqNHu3M1gE0B2GLJLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=fa989711\" target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/qFTfqpc</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">「入咗台嘅巴絲打記住要開notification 方便追蹤本台最新消息」</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f28d0da8c008d6bbd0c48348327ff0d92b0213","tid":1116621,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T06:35:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e11ba998f4145a9637dd2a1011304b78f2da246","tid":1116621,"uid":231293,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T06:42:23.000Z","msg":"毒撚先用discard<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eb46aa7842439599a65230bf43696e5ab2bceae","tid":1116621,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e11ba998f4145a9637dd2a1011304b78f2da246","tid":1116621,"uid":231293,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T06:42:23.000Z","msg":"毒撚先用discard<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T06:49:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d91546708c52dc7adfd869d8bafdda62a8df03fc","tid":1116621,"uid":170375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T06:52:05.000Z","msg":"Fredbot"},{"pid":"58b6b466998ac2c76e617013e297952b88109417","tid":1116621,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d91546708c52dc7adfd869d8bafdda62a8df03fc","tid":1116621,"uid":170375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T06:52:05.000Z","msg":"Fredbot"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T06:56:27.000Z","msg":"用緊第二個啊"},{"pid":"f9acdc1455ead9c989cff161f7ef347549d7f2f8","tid":1116621,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T07:03:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fac